ssTFTP v0.2 (24-11-2008):
 -> Support for TFTP Option Extension (RFC 2347)
 -> Support for TFTP Blocksize Option (RFC 2348)
 -> Refactor client and server to ease their configuration
 -> Several bug fixes

ssTFTP v0.1 (20-11-2008):
 -> Implementation of TFTP client and server according to the standard RFC 1350
